dct_title_s: Croatia city graphic 1:12,500. Rijeka. Series M903
dct_description_sm: Alteranate title: Rijeka.Transverse Mercator projection. Relief shown by 20 meter contour interval and spot elevation. This sheet falls within NL 33-8, 1501, 1:250,000 and 2085-1, 2135-IV, M709, 1:50,000. Relief shown by contour lines and spot elevations. "WGS 84." With a glossary. "Map information as of 1993." Inset: map of area (1:200,000). "Printed by NIMA 9-97."
